  ('dietitian-moex-11276', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列那些是可以使用靜脈營養的狀況？ 食慾不振導致攝食不足   腸道阻塞不通   腸道營養供應量不 足時   嚴重的胰臟發炎', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "85ba92118f33", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "112", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 11, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11277', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關身體遭受重大壓力時會造成代謝上之改變的敘述，何者錯誤？ glucose生成增加造成血糖上升 細胞激素分泌增加引起肌肉組織分解 catecholamine及cortisol分泌增加促使脂肪合成增加 aldosterone分泌增加促使腎小管對水分之吸收增加', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "85ba92118f33", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "112", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 12, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11278', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '若某位病患的呼吸氣體分析，其呼吸商為0.72，則其體內的營養素利用主要來自： 碳水化合物    脂肪 蛋白質    三大營養素', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "85ba92118f33", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "112", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 13, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11279', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關中央靜脈營養支持的敘述，何者正確？ 可適用於手術後腸阻塞無法使用腸道之患者 用於腸道功能正常，但食慾不振的患者 是一種短期的營養支持方式 與週邊靜脈營養相比是較為安全的營養支持方式', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "85ba92118f33", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "112", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
